{
    "headline": "<h2>Gameplay Features</h2>",
    "content": "<p>Eggomatic might have a standard 5x3 reel and 20 paylines, but don't let that fool you! It's the eggciting bonus features that make this game stand out from the coop. The EggOMatic machine on the right side of the screen cracks out eggs with varying values along a conveyor belt. And who doesn't love a good conveyor belt? It's like sushi, but for eggs!</p>

    <p>If the stars align and a wild symbol links up with an egg, the player cracks open that baby to reveal a corresponding value. The only thing better than finding money in an egg is finding a chicken that lays golden eggs!</p>

